    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The Roman Catholic term Stadtpfarrkirche (municipal parish church) is roughly equivalent to the Protestant Stadtkirche and refers to churches that represent a particular autonomy of a city in political significance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
